    "result": {"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h3>호이스팅</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>- 자바스크립트 엔진은 소스코드를 한 줄씩 순차적으로 실행하기 앞서, 변수 선언을 포함한 모든 선언문을 찾아내 먼저 실행한다.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>-> var, let, const, function, function*, class 키워드는 모두 호이스팅</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>단, 변수 선언과 값 할당은 실행 시점이 다르다. 변수 선언은 런타임 이전에 실행되지만, 값 할당은 순차적으로 실행되는 런타임에 실행.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h3>var</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>- ES6전 변수 선언을 할 수 있으며 동시에 할당도 가능. 하지만, var의 문제점으로 인해 let과 const가 등장하였다.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>var 문제점</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>- 변수 중복 선언 가능 -> 예기치 못한 값을 반환 할 수 있다.</li>\n<li>- 함수 레벨 스코프로 인해 함수 외부에서 선언한 변수는 모두 전역 변수</li>\n<li>- 변수 선언 이전에 변수를 참조하면 언제나 undefined를 반환</li>\n</ul>\n<hr/>\n<p>let과 const 키워드는 위 문제점을 해결해 준다.</p>\n<br/>\n<h3>1. 변수 중복 선언 불가</h3>\n<h6>let</h6>\n<ul>\n<li>- 변수 중복 선언이 불가하지만, 재할당은 가능</li>\n</ul>\n<h6>const</h6>\n<ul>\n<li>- let과 다른 점은 반드시 선언과 초기화를 동시에 진행해야한다.</li>\n<li>- const는 상수로 재선언과 재할당 모두 불가</li>\n</ul>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container github-light-theme grvsc-ps-t4tStz\" data-language=\"javascript\" data-index=\"0\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-5 grvsc-t4tStz-9\">let</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\"> val </span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-9\">=</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\"> </span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-8 grvsc-t4tStz-10\">&#39;hello&#39;</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-5 grvsc-t4tStz-9\">let</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\"> val </span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-9\">=</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\"> </span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-8 grvsc-t4tStz-10\">&#39;bye&#39;</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">;</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-6 grvsc-t4tStz-2\">// syntaxError</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">val </span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-9\">=</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\"> </span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-8 grvsc-t4tStz-10\">&#39;bye&#39;</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-5 grvsc-t4tStz-9\">const</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\"> </span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-7 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">val</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">;</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-6 grvsc-t4tStz-2\">//SyntaxError</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-5 grvsc-t4tStz-9\">const</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\"> </span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-7 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">val</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\"> </span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-9\">=</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\"> </span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-8 grvsc-t4tStz-10\">&#39;hello&#39;</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-5 grvsc-t4tStz-9\">const</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\"> </span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-7 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">val</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\"> </span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-9\">=</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\"> </span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-8 grvsc-t4tStz-10\">&#39;bye&#39;</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">;</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-6 grvsc-t4tStz-2\">// TypeError</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<h3>2. 블록 레벨 스코프</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>- let과 const 키워드로 선언한 변수는 모두 코드 블록을 지역 스코프로 인정하는 블록 레벨 스코프를 따른다.</li>\n</ul>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container github-light-theme grvsc-ps-t4tStz\" data-language=\"javascript\" data-index=\"1\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-5 grvsc-t4tStz-9\">let</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\"> a </span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-9\">=</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\"> </span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-7 grvsc-t4tStz-3\">1</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-5 grvsc-t4tStz-9\">if</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">(</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-7 grvsc-t4tStz-3\">true</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">){</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">  </span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-5 grvsc-t4tStz-9\">let</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\"> a </span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-9\">=</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\"> </span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-7 grvsc-t4tStz-3\">2</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">}</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-7 grvsc-t4tStz-3\">console</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">.</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-7 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">log</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">(a);</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-6 grvsc-t4tStz-2\">//1</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<h3>3. 변수 호이스팅</h3>\n<h6>let</h6>\n<ul>\n<li>- let 키워드로 선언한 변수는 선언 단계와 초기화 단계가 분리되어 진행된다. 즉, 런타임 이전에 자바스크립트 엔진에 의해 선언 단계가 먼저 실행되지만, 초기화 단계가 실행되지 않았을 때 해당 변수에 접근하려고 하면 참조 에러가 뜬다.</li>\n</ul>\n<h6>const</h6>\n<ul>\n<li>- const 키워드는 선언 단계와 초기화 단계가 동시에 진행된다.</li>\n</ul>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container github-light-theme grvsc-ps-t4tStz\" data-language=\"javascript\" data-index=\"2\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-7 grvsc-t4tStz-3\">console</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">.</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-7 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">log</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">(a);</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-6 grvsc-t4tStz-2\">// ReferenceError: a is not defined</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-5 grvsc-t4tStz-9\">let</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\"> a </span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-9\">=</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\"> </span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-8 grvsc-t4tStz-10\">&#39;hello&#39;</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-7 grvsc-t4tStz-3\">console</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">.</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-7 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">log</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">(b);</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-6 grvsc-t4tStz-2\">//ReferenceError: Cannot access &#39;b&#39; before initialization</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-5 grvsc-t4tStz-9\">const</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\"> </span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-7 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">b</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\"> </span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-9\">=</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\"> </span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-8 grvsc-t4tStz-10\">&#39;bye&#39;</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">;</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<style class=\"grvsc-styles\">\n  .grv